texts.text: >An underground facility somewhere in the city...
What? No way!
*Laugh*
>A group of demons make pleasant conversation...
Those?
3, 4... Plenty to go around... You sure we're all good?
No problem. Just do what I say and you'll be rich bastards in no time.
But do exactly as I say.
Yes, boss!
...We all in position? Just like we planned.
Copy.
>The man throws something into the group of demons.
...? What's this...?
*Scream*
W-What?! I can't see...
Go! Everyone go!!
*Groan*
Shit, I still can't see anything!
Huh?! Who are you?!
No stop!
Got it!
Me too!
That flash of light...
Girls? What happened? Someone say something!
Hey! Got another one here!
Don't lose it! Get the gem before it regains its sight!
>The demon flies high into the air!
Damn, we're too late... It's gone.
Who are you people?! Everyone...!
I guess you can't fight back as long as we have these.
It's very interesting. You'll listen to anything we say now, right?
B-but...
Wait, they stole everyone's garnets...?!
Screw it. Hey, boss! We're using the demons!
...Copy. But stay sharp.
I don't care if the demon dies as long as the gems are unblemished.
Copy that!
*Glub*
*Snicker*
*Chuckle*
Demons... I see, they're summoners.
There's... So many. I can't do this alone...
Gah...! Where the hell did it go?!
Go after it! Let's get its gem and get outta here!
Everyone, please hold on... I'll come back with help!
I'm not letting these despicable humans get their way!
Shit, can't find it...
What now? It's already been 2 days!
Doesn't matter. Summon another demon and get searching.
But if we summon too many demons around here it might be...
Just do it! You're such a pain...!
*Growl*
Oh, hunting demons again are we.
Alright then. Go find that...
Hey, we're right on time.
Finding them on the first day has to mean our luck is pretty good right now.
Hey, pal. Care to explain why you're summoning demons in public like this?
There were traces of summoning all around here too.
That was you, correct?
Well, well... Here they are. The Liberators!
Let's dance... Demons! Go!
Honey was just politely asking what you were up to. So rude!
He might be feeling guilty. Getting pissed during questioning usually means that.
Then let's get ready too! Devil Download!
Yeah! We won!
Yay!
Piece of cake.
Haha, yay! High five, Newbie!
Everything's easy when Honey's around.
But what were they up to though...?
Even when we tried asking, Jeng Yun just ended up choking him out.
I may've overdone it. I apologize.
It's all good. It's his fault for struggling  so much.
An ex-Acolyte with probably nothing worth saying either.
An ex-Acolyte... Really?
Yeah. He summoned just like an Acolyte would.
But for now, let's take care of this trash...
...As long as I can stay hidden like this, things might work out.
But who were those summoners? They didn't look like backup or anything.
Anyways. Managed to lose those other humans at least.
And now I need to figure out how to get our gems back...
...! I wonder if they can be useful.
They look strong and might be able to deal with the humans back at the den,
Steal back our garnets and save everyone.
And we can get rid of them afterwards...!
Plus... Those machines. They look like the source of their power too.
Then let's do that. I'll let everyone back home know.
>Something strange catches your eye,
>and a shadow dives down to attack Jeng Yun!
Jeng Yun!
Watch out!
*Wince*
>Jeng Yun tries to counter with an arm block.
>The shadow latches onto his arm, hesitates and decides to fly away.
It gave up. You okay?
Don't worry about me. However...
It took my phone.
A demon that steals phones? That's a new one.
Maybe it's that other guy's friend?
They could be. I won't deny that possibility.
...You need this, don't you?
If you want it back in one piece, do as I say!
A demon making demands on a Dx2? Who the hell do you think you are?
>The demon uses her talon-like feet to slowly crush Jeng Yun's phone.
Hey, slow down. You're gonna kill the hostage before making any demands?
What do you want?
Human suddenly intruded my den. Our den.
My friends were captured by them.
Do something about them and save my friends.
Wow. Wasn't expecting that twist.
So those guys were looking for her.
Human invading your home... I see.
And you're using humans to get rid of other humans.
And if we say no?
...I'll smash this thing to bits.
(This is the source of their power, so they have to say yes!)
...Okay. We'll help you.
Hey, Jeng Yun...!
The summoning app is still shrouded in mystery, but Shiang Sun said this.
Even if the app is downloaded onto a new phone,
there's no way to know if you'll get the same demons back from before.
We should make sure these machines aren't put in too much danger.
Right.
Time for a surprise attack.
Thank you for understanding!
...I don't think so, Newbie.
Yeah. Even before we summon any demons,
she'll destroy Jeng Yun's phone.
And if the Acolytes are involved,
we'll need to investigate anyways.
Alright, fine...
That settles it. Please lead us to your den.
Okay. follow me...
